text: Belaid Abdessalam () (20 July 1928 - 27 June 2020) was an Algerian politician. He served as Prime Minister of Algeria. He served as minister from 8 July 1992 until he resigned in 21 August 1993. Abdessalam was born in Dehemcha, near Sétif, Algeria on 20 July 1928. He died on 27 June 2020, aged 91.Décès de l'ancien chef du gouvernement Belaïd Abdesselam ==References== Category:1928 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Prime ministers of Algeria
